{"tid":2389492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：發現有人攞熱血公民報考警察、網上報案指一些地點違反限聚令。我地會去差館備案。","createTime":"2021-02-01T03:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T03:36:39.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58cff5523e39688bb73ed919b8710cec5d817b46","tid":2389492,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0evvoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0evvoi.jpg&h=7bd0b3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：<br />\n先前發現有人攞熱血公民的電郵報考警察，我無理會。<br />\n今日收到一個網上報案的查詢，又有人用我們的電郵胡亂點了一些地點篤灰，指其違反限聚令。 <br />\n我地會去差館備案；搞平民百姓生活、打爛街坊糊口的人，是應該落地獄的。"},{"pid":"1c1ed27d78143ead3f930d0557e6a88216fce70e","tid":2389492,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"又唔見啲人玩奶共黨班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f262ebb67be2b3e5adae1349336e2a6f9633a96","tid":2389492,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八自己攞嚟衰"},{"pid":"0b1034326c5ef56166ba1d9460dcdb4c4c4e12d0","tid":2389492,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c1ed27d78143ead3f930d0557e6a88216fce70e","tid":2389492,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"又唔見啲人玩奶共黨班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}